title: Stars over Clarion celebrates landmark with special show (Clarion University of Pennsylvania)
text: ( Source : Clarion University of Pennsylvania ) Clarion graduate student William Snyder ('15), will celebrate two years of Stars Over Clarion, a planetarium show he created and produces, at 7 p.m. Nov. 5 in Peirce Planetarium , Grunenwald
